column8: Imported

Made for All Pro Von Miller to help shed blocks and rack up sacks, these junior sized, light and supportive cleats, have a higher cut with a strong, protective upper and a rubber molded plate for a comfortable feel.

Detachable sprintcleat stud technology creates a shoe that sets the industry standard for light weight"
